<i>adverb</i>: 확고히 [확꼬히], 탄탄히 [탄탄히], 철석같이 [철썩까치], 질끈 [질끈], 지독히 [지도키], 지독스레 [지독쓰레], 의연히 [의연히], 분명히 [분명히], 딱딱 [딱딱], 딱 [딱], 든든히 [든든히], 단호히 [단ː호히], 단단히 [단단히], 꿋꿋이 [꾿꾸시], 꾹꾹 [꾹꾹], 꾹 [꾹], 꽉꽉 [꽉꽉], 꽉 [꽉], 꼿꼿이 [꼳꼬시], 꼭꼭 [꼭꼭], 꼭 [꼭], 굳건히 [굳껀히], 공고히 [공고히], 견고히 [견고히], 강경히 [강경히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>확고히 [확꼬히]</dt><br>
<dd>firmly; determinedly; unshakably</dd><br>
<dd>태도나 상황 등이 확실하고 굳세게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's attitude or situation, etc., being clear and unchanging.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>탄탄히 [탄탄히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stoutly; firmly; robustly</dd><br>
<dd>무르거나 느슨하지 않고 아주 단단하고 굳세게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a solid and strong manner that is not soft or loose.</dd><br>
<dd>2. stoutly</dd><br>
<dd>조직이나 기구 등이 쉽게 무너지거나 흔들리지 않는 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner in which an organization, group, etc., does not shake or collapse easily.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>철석같이 [철썩까치]</dt><br>
<dd>firmly; unwaveringly; resolutely</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 의지, 약속 등이 쇠와 돌처럼 매우 굳고 단단하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's mind, will, word, etc., being very firm and steadfast just like iron and stone.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>질끈 [질끈]</dt><br>
<dd>1. tightly; firmly</dd><br>
<dd>단단히 졸라매는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of fastening something tightly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. tightly; firmly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 주어 벌어진 사이를 눌러 붙이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of pressing things together tightly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>지독히 [지도키]</dt><br>
<dd>1. spitefully; venomously</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 성격이 매우 모질고 독하며 매섭게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's mind or personality being very cold and harsh.</dd><br>
<dd>2. potently; strongly</dd><br>
<dd>맛이나 냄새 등이 해롭거나 참기 어려울 정도로 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of the taste, smell, etc., being intolerably harmful or strong.</dd><br>
<dd>3. extremely; incredibly</dd><br>
<dd>날씨나 기온 등이 일정한 정도를 넘은 정도로.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of weather, climate, etc., being beyond a certain degree.</dd><br>
<dd>4. extremely; incredibly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 모양이나 상태 등이 극에 달한 정도로.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of an appearance or situation being very extreme.</dd><br>
<dd>5. severely</dd><br>
<dd>병이 더할 수 없을 정도로 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of illness or soreness being severe beyond words.</dd><br>
<dd>6. firmly</dd><br>
<dd>의지나 마음이 매우 크고 강하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of a person's having a strong will.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>지독스레 [지독쓰레]</dt><br>
<dd>1. spitefully; venomously</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 성격이 매우 모질고 독하며 매서운 데가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's mind or personality being very cold and harsh.</dd><br>
<dd>2. potently; strongly</dd><br>
<dd>맛이나 냄새 등이 해롭거나 참기 어려울 정도로 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of the taste, smell, etc., being intolerably harmful or strong.</dd><br>
<dd>3. extremely; incredibly</dd><br>
<dd>날씨나 기온 등이 일정한 정도를 넘은 데가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of weather, climate, etc., being beyond a certain degree.</dd><br>
<dd>4. extremely; incredibly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 모양이나 상태 등이 극에 달한 데가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of an appearance or situation being very extreme.</dd><br>
<dd>5. severely</dd><br>
<dd>병이 더할 수 없을 정도로 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of illness or soreness being severe beyond words.</dd><br>
<dd>6. firmly</dd><br>
<dd>의지나 마음이 매우 크고 강한 데가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of a person's having a strong will.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>의연히 [의연히]</dt><br>
<dd>resolutely; firmly; unwaveringly</dd><br>
<dd>의지가 굳세어서 어떤 상황에서도 끄떡없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without being daunted under any circumstances because one's will is strong.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>분명히 [분명히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. clearly</dd><br>
<dd>모습, 소리 등이 흐릿하지 않고 또렷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a clear appearance, sound, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. firmly</dd><br>
<dd>태도, 목표 등이 확실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Set on a clear attitude, goal, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>3. surely</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사실이 틀림이 없이 확실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>(a fact being confirmed) Certainly and accurately.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>딱딱 [딱딱]</dt><br>
<dd>1. broad</dd><br>
<dd>여럿이 다 또는 잇따라 가슴, 어깨가 바라지거나 눈, 입이 활짝 벌어진 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which all of several people straighten up their shoulders, puff their chests out, or open their eyes or mouths wide at the same time or in succession.</dd><br>
<dd>2. precisely</dd><br>
<dd>여럿이 다 수량이나 크기, 상황 등이 정확하게 맞는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which all of several things are in harmony precisely in number, amount, size, situation, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>3. one after another; at once</dd><br>
<dd>여럿이 다 또는 잇따라 마주치는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of several people or things running into one another at the same time or in succession.</dd><br>
<dd>4. strongly</dd><br>
<dd>여럿이 다 또는 잇따라 움직이지 않고 굳세게 버티는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which several people or things stand firmly without moving, at the same time or in succession.</dd><br>
<dd>5. firmly</dd><br>
<dd>여럿이 다 또는 잇따라 단단히 달라붙은 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which several things stick to something tightly at the same time or in succession.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>딱 [딱]</dt><br>
<dd>1. broad</dd><br>
<dd>가슴, 어깨가 바라지거나 눈, 입이 활짝 벌어진 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which one's chest and shoulders are wide, or one's eyes and mouth are open wide.</dd><br>
<dd>2. precisely</dd><br>
<dd>수량이나 크기, 상황 등이 정확하게 맞는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being correct in number, amount, size, situation, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>3. all of a sudden</dd><br>
<dd>갑자기 마주치는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of meeting with someone or something suddenly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. strongly</dd><br>
<dd>움직이지 않고 굳세게 버티는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of standing firmly without moving.</dd><br>
<dd>5. firmly</dd><br>
<dd>단단히 달라붙은 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of adhering tightly to something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>든든히 [든든히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. reassuringly</dd><br>
<dd>무엇에 대한 믿음으로 의지가 되고 마음이 놓이게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that makes someone feel secure and rely on someone on the basis of trust in him/her.</dd><br>
<dd>2. strongly; robustly</dd><br>
<dd>물건이나 몸이 알차고 야무지게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which an object or body is solid and sturdy.</dd><br>
<dd>3. reliably</dd><br>
<dd>믿을 만할 정도로 알차고 실하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being so solid and substantial as to be reliable.</dd><br>
<dd>4. strongly; firmly</dd><br>
<dd>품은 생각이나 뜻이 강하고 야무지게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which one's ambition or wish is firm and strong.</dd><br>
<dd>5. fully</dd><br>
<dd>먹은 것이나 입은 것이 충분하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of eating or wearing enough.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단호히 [단ː호히]</dt><br>
<dd>firmly; flatly</dd><br>
<dd>결심이나 태도, 입장 등이 흔들림 없이 엄격하고 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a stern and clear manner without being shaken from a decision, attitude, position, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단단히 [단단히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. hard</dd><br>
<dd>사물이 어떤 힘에 의해 모양이 변하지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>(an object) Hard enough not to be changed by a certain force.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hard; solidly</dd><br>
<dd>약하거나 무르지 않고 빈틈이 없이 튼튼하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Evenly solid, not weakly or softly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. firmly</dd><br>
<dd>속이 꽉 차서 야무지고 실속이 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>Fully, firmly, and practically.</dd><br>
<dd>4. tightly; firmly</dd><br>
<dd>느슨하지 않고 튼튼하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Strongly, not loosely.</dd><br>
<dd>5. surely; strongly</dd><br>
<dd>뜻이나 생각이 흔들림 없이 강하게.</dd><br>
<dd>(one's will or thought maintained) Strongly, without being shaken.</dd><br>
<dd>6. seriously; severely</dd><br>
<dd>보통보다 더 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>More severely than normal.</dd><br>
<dd>7. surely</dd><br>
<dd>확실하게 제대로.</dd><br>
<dd>Done surely.</dd><br>
<dd>8. strongly</dd><br>
<dd>일의 기본 바탕이 튼튼하게.</dd><br>
<dd>(the ground for something made) Strongly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>꿋꿋이 [꾿꾸시]</dt><br>
<dd>firmly; strongly</dd><br>
<dd>어려움에도 불구하고 마음이나 뜻, 태도가 굳세고 곧게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a strong and righteous mind, will, or attitude in the face of difficulties.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>꾹꾹 [꾹꾹]</dt><br>
<dd>1. firmly; hard</dd><br>
<dd>잇따라 또는 매우 힘을 주어 누르거나 조이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of pressing down, gripping, or tightening very strongly or repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. patiently; stoically</dd><br>
<dd>잇따라 또는 몹시 힘을 들여 참거나 견디는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of enduring or bearing very painfully or repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. completely</dd><br>
<dd>아주 단단히 숨거나 어떤 곳에 들어가서 나오지 않는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of hiding or not entirely coming out of a place.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>꾹 [꾹]</dt><br>
<dd>1. firmly; hard</dd><br>
<dd>매우 힘주어 세게 누르거나 잡거나 조이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of pressing down, gripping, or tightening very strongly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. patiently; stoically</dd><br>
<dd>매우 애써서 힘들게 참거나 견디는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of enduring or bearing very painfully.</dd><br>
<dd>3. completely</dd><br>
<dd>조금도 보이지 않게 숨거나 한 곳에서 나오지 않는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of hiding or not coming out of a place so as not to be seen.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>꽉꽉 [꽉꽉]</dt><br>
<dd>1. firmly; strongly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 힘껏 여러 번 힘을 주는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of applying pressure very hard a couple of times.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fully; compactly</dd><br>
<dd>빈틈없이 가득 들어차거나 막힌 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being packed or crammed to the full.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>꽉 [꽉]</dt><br>
<dd>1. firmly; strongly; tight</dd><br>
<dd>힘껏 힘주는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word mimicking the manner of appying pressure very hard.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fully; compactly</dd><br>
<dd>가득하거나 많은 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of being full of, or packed with something.</dd><br>
<dd>3. tight</dd><br>
<dd>꼭 맞거나 작은 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of being fitting too tightly or too small.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>꼿꼿이 [꼳꼬시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. straight; upright</dd><br>
<dd>사람의 자세나 서 있는 사물이 굽지 않고 곧게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of one's posture or a standing object being erect, not bent.</dd><br>
<dd>2. firmly; honestly</dd><br>
<dd>사람의 마음가짐이나 성격이 곧고 굳세게.</dd><br>
<dd>With an honest and strong mindset or personality.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>꼭꼭 [꼭꼭]</dt><br>
<dd>1. firmly; tightly</dd><br>
<dd>잇따라 힘주어 세게 누르거나 잡는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of pressing repeatedly or holding strongly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. patiently; stoically</dd><br>
<dd>잇따라 힘들여 참거나 견디는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of painfully enduring or bearing one after another.</dd><br>
<dd>3. completely</dd><br>
<dd>잇따라 보이지 않게 숨거나 한 곳에서 나오지 않는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of repeatedly hiding or not coming out of a place so as not to be seen.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>꼭 [꼭]</dt><br>
<dd>1. firmly; tightly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것을 빈틈이 없이 힘주어 세게 누르거나 잡는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of pressing or holding something strongly and fast.</dd><br>
<dd>2. patiently; stoically</dd><br>
<dd>애써서 힘들여 참거나 견디는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of enduring or bearing something in spite of pain.</dd><br>
<dd>3. completely</dd><br>
<dd>보이지 않게 숨거나 한 곳에서 나오지 않는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of hiding or not coming out of a place so as not to be seen.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>굳건히 [굳껀히]</dt><br>
<dd>firmly; unshakably</dd><br>
<dd>굳세고 튼튼하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Strongly and solidly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>공고히 [공고히]</dt><br>
<dd>firmly</dd><br>
<dd>굳고 단단하고 튼튼하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Solidly, hard, and strongly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>견고히 [견고히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. solidly; robustly</dd><br>
<dd>단단하고 튼튼하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Hard and strongly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. firmly; unshakably</dd><br>
<dd>흔들림이 없이 굳세고 확고히.</dd><br>
<dd>With firm determination and without being shaken.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>강경히 [강경히]</dt><br>
<dd>strongly; firmly</dd><br>
<dd>태도나 주장 등을 타협하거나 양보하지 않을 정도로 강하게.</dd><br>
<dd>So strongly that compromise or concession is not allowed in one's attitude or opinion.</dd><br>
